msgctxt "sn45.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Vihāravagga "
msgstr "2. Meditation "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Paṭhamaparisuddhasutta "
msgstr "16. Purified (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.16:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.16:1.2"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā parisuddhā pariyodātā anaṅgaṇā vigatūpakkilesā anuppannā uppajjanti, nāññatra tathāgatassa pātubhāvā arahato sammāsambuddhassa. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these eight things don’t arise to be purified, bright, flawless, and rid of corruptions except when a Realized One, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha has appeared. "

msgctxt "sn45.16:1.3"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "sn45.16:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "They are: right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.16:1.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā parisuddhā pariyodātā anaṅgaṇā vigatūpakkilesā anuppannā uppajjanti, nāññatra tathāgatassa pātubhāvā arahato sammāsambuddhassā”ti. "
msgstr "These eight things don’t arise to be purified, bright, flawless, and rid of corruptions except when a Realized One, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha has appeared.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.16:1.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

